title: Top Five Biggest Red Flags From ‘Love Is Blind’ Season 2
description:
Amelia and Juliet are back after their finale discussion with Bill Simmons and Kevin O’Connor to go through some of the most cringe-worthy moments of ‘Love Is Blind’ Season 2 and the top five biggest red flags from the show. 
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Juliet Litman
Producers: Sasha Ashall and Chelsea Stark-Jones
